                <para>
                    <title>Truck, RE Bus, SFC Bus, and Stripped Chassis Service Information</title>
                </para>
                <para>The new upper oil pan assembly has retained the offset and removed the center bosses with mounting
                    bolt holes (see Figure 2). The new assembly is compatible with all engines using upper oil pan with
                    offset feature. The old mounting bolts (M6 x 25) can be reused. The old center boss mounting bolts
                    (M8 x 40) can be discarded.
                </para>
                <para>To install new upper oil pan assembly, follow procedures outlined in corresponding Model Year
                    Engine Service Manual. Installation procedures remain the same, with the exception of eliminating
                    center boss mounting bolts.
                </para>
